        {
            "title": "半日收市︱跌勢暫緩 恒指跌11點報26552點 泡泡瑪特變身藍籌最強",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股今早走勢反覆，一度連20天線亦失守，中段逐步收復失地，半日微跌收場。泡泡瑪特(09992)昨天出手回購，該股今早即變身表現最佳藍籌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250714_FI_source-web_09992-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250714_FI_source-web_09992-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早低開19點，初段原本反覆偏好，一度衝上26638點，升74點，未幾便掉頭下滑，中段最多曾跌200點，低見26363點，失守20天線(最新約為26281點)，其後迅速反彈，後段曾短暫轉升，早市逾半時間跌幅僅數十點。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250714_FI_source-web_09992-4.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250714_FI_source-web_09992-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240430_FI_source-web_00005-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240430_FI_source-web_00005-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：滙控官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250428_FI_source-web_09992-2-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250428_FI_source-web_09992-2-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250714_FI_source-web_09992-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240430_FI_source-web_00005-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：滙控官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250428_FI_source-web_09992-2-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指中午收報26552點，跌11點或0.04%。恒生科技指數明顯跑輸大市，跌38點或0.66%，報5711點；國企指數跌11點或0.12%，報9123點。主板半日成交1298.45億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日跌14點，報26574點，高水22點。科指期貨跌35點，報5720點，高水8點。國指期貨跌17點，報9128點，高水5點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股6.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金融與地產股再成今早撐市功臣，滙控(00005)回升1.58%，報129元，單一股份已令恒指跌少近38點。兩隻藍籌內險股亦回升，中國人壽(02628)漲3.37%，報33.1元；中國平安(02318)升1.1%，報69.15元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生地產分類指數10隻成分股幾乎全升，尤以內房及物管股最為突出。華潤萬象生活(01209)漲3.85%，報43.72元；同系華潤置地(01109)升3.92%，報29.7元。中國海外(00688)升4%，報13.77元；龍湖(00960)也升1.78%，報9.7元。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240430_FI_source-web_00005-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240430_FI_source-web_00005-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">泡泡瑪特昨天動用逾2.51億元入市回購，消息曝光後今早股價應聲彈升，最高曾逼近200元關口，高見199.6元，飆10.4%，半日低位190.2元時也升5.2%；中午收報196.1元，仍漲8.46%，半日成交已達42.47億元，在主板股份成交額榜上排第3位。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">摩根士丹利也就泡泡瑪特回購發報告，指出該公司對上一次回購已是2024年2月，認為泡泡瑪特現正處於強勁增長階段，具備明確的驅動力與長期故事，相信今輪回購或可引來一直等待股價催化劑的投資者關注；重申對該股「增持」評級，目標價325元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250428_FI_source-web_09992-2-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250428_FI_source-web_09992-2-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅科股跌多於升，「ATMXJ」中便有4位成員報跌，騰訊(00700)與小米(01810)跌幅均逾1%，其中騰訊跌1.48%，報601元；小米也跌1.48%，報35.94元，見6個月低位。單是騰訊與小米，合共已拖低恒指約46點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)則微跌0.25%，報160元；美團(03690)跌0.66%，報97.85元。昨天逆市造好的百度(09888)，今早回吐1.49%，報145.2元。芯片股續受壓，中芯國際(00981)跌2.86%，報74.8元；華虹半導體(01347)離開「紅底股」行列，半日跌3.02%，報99.5元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">生科藥業股延續昨天弱勢，藥明康德(02359)跌4.55%，報113.2元，成表現最差藍籌；同系藥明生物(02269)跌2.22%，報37.02元。翰森製藥(03692)也跌3.39%，報39.88元。</p>\n</div>",
